## 11. Out of Scope (for the current version)

- MCP server, Redis, heartbeat — removed entirely
- Autonomous agent execution (no runners, no headless CLI invocation)
- Automatic conflict detection between service plans
- Web UI for session visualization
- Multi-round negotiation between agents